      <title>英国监管机构下调经济增长预期后，里夫斯陷入赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/reeves-is-in-the-red-after-uk-watchdog-downgrades-growth-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府财政监管机构下调经济增长预测后，雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 面临不得不削减开支的新风险，这使得英国财政大臣在下个月发布重要报告时忙于满足预算规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/reeves-is-in-the-red-after-uk-watchdog-downgrades-growth-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
